  <brief_title>Evaluation of the Safety and Efficacy of Vardenafil in Subjects With Erectile Dysfunction</brief_title>
  <official_title>Open-label, Multi-centre, Study to Investigate the Safety, Tolerability and Efficacy of Flexible Doses of Vardenafil Given on Demand in Males With Erectile Dysfunction</official_title>
